				<DIV>I am a human magician. This is to let you know that Barrenzin's 4th task directs me to <STRONG>East</STRONG> Commonlands to kill Dervish Cutthroats, and more. I spent several hours looking for DCs in East Commonlands, to no avail. I eventually crossed over to West Commonlands and, lo and behold, was able to find the DC's and carry out all the 4th-task requirements there ---- in <STRONG>West</STRONG> Commonlands. Obviously, I was misdirected. The task took place in West Commonlands, not East Commonlands.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Having completed the 4th task and reaped its rewards, I expected&nbsp;Barrenzin to give me a 5th task. Instead he gave the 4th task once again, which I completed a second time (no rewards, of course). So I went back to Barrenzin and, to my surprise, he gave me&nbsp;his 6th and 7th tasks ---- but no&nbsp;5th task. I completed both the 6th and 7th tasks and Barrenzin now says he has no more tasks for 'someone of my abilities'. </DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>So where do I go next to get more tasks?</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>To summarize, the <STRONG>4th task </STRONG>takes place in <STRONG>West Commonlands</STRONG>, not East Commonlands. Secondly,&nbsp;Barrenzin does <STRONG>not</STRONG> offer&nbsp;a <STRONG>5th task</STRONG>. (I need chest armour and I would have thought the 5th task would have given me that.) Thirdly, I don't know where to go next to get more tasks. </DIV>
