<DIV>Barrenzin does offer a 5th Trial - however it is a Group Trial (need at least 2 members - not sure if it is minimum level driven or average level driven, but I believe the minimum level is 15) - Use the Keyword "Group" and you should be able to get the task (assuming you have the approprate group). Note: you will have the same issues with the 8th and 9th trial - those are group tasks as well.</FONT></DIV>
<DIV></FONT>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Have you done Castelen Drewe's Armor quests? If not, those are another possibility.</FONT></DIV>
				
